root: ^This happened to me but no one believes

^Trapped in an elevator. The air is getting thin. The air is getting… Steamy?!?!?! This self-insert situational erotica places you in the role of a repairman trapped in an elevator with the big-time CEO of the company you work under. Her charm and excitement for the elevator industry has always had you smitten. Seduce her in time and you might just have a new girlfriend by the time help arrives and gets you out…
